<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using Zend_Captcha_ReCaptcha, I try to pass options to ReCaptcha to be able to change the language, which is not working :</p>

<p>$captcha = new Zend_Captcha_ReCaptcha();</p>

<p>$captcha-&gt;setPubkey('MyPubKey');
$captcha-&gt;setPrivkey('MyPrivKey');</p>

<p>$captcha-&gt;setOption('lang', 'fr');</p>

<p>echo $captcha-&gt;render();</p>

<p>Displays ReCaptcha in english instead of french</p>

<p>Can be worked around using :</p>

<p>$captcha-&gt;getService()-&gt;setOption('lang', 'fr');</p>

